dcterms:description: The dataset is described as the market data of constituent stocks in the Shenzhen Stock Exchange Component Index, which was first released on January 23rd, 1995.
dcterms:title: Shenzhen Stock Exchange Component Index (SZSE COMP)

dcterms:description: The dataset consists of daily returns of 38 constituent stocks of the SZSE COMP from January 1st, 2013 to July 12th, 2017.
dcterms:title: Daily returns of SZSE COMP constituent stocks
